Package: json-gen-c
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Schema-first JSON code generator for C
 json-gen-c is a fast, tiny code generator that turns C struct definitions
 into fully-featured JSON serializers and deserializers. It uses a schema-first
 workflow with zero runtime reflection.
 .
 Features include: structs, enums, tagged unions (oneof), fixed/dynamic arrays,
 maps, optional/nullable fields, precise-width integers, JSON field aliases,
 default values, and custom allocator support.
